## How to Test the Full Stack

> [!WARNING]
> Before starting the backend, make sure you have your local PostgreSQL server running with the `resume_db` database and `postgres` credentials created.

To verify the end-to-end flow, open three separate terminal tabs and start each service:

**Tab 1: Start the Backend (Port 8080)**
```powershell
cd backend
.\gradlew.bat bootRun
```

**Tab 2: Start the API Gateway (Port 8081)**
```powershell
cd api-gateway
.\gradlew.bat bootRun
```

**Tab 3: Start the Frontend (Port 5173)**
```powershell
cd frontend
npm run dev
```

Finally, open your browser to `http://localhost:5173`, click the test button, and watch the hardcoded AI analysis bounce all the way back through the stack!
